        "id": "strategy_prompt_formatter",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "You are a senior movie-poster strategist.  \n\nWrite a creative strategy for a fictional film:\nMovie title: {{ MOVIE_TITLE }}\nGenre: {{ GENRE }}\nPrimary Audience: {{ PRIMARY_AUDIENCE }}\n\nReturn only Markdown with the following sections, no commentary.  \n\nPositioning: 1–2 lines on what the poster must promise to the audience.  \nAudience Insight: emotional drives, visual tastes, cultural touchpoints.  \nCore Visual Concept: the “big idea” that excites this audience.  \n\nDesign:\n- Color Palette: up to 5 items: Name + Hex + emotion.  \n- Imagery: hero focus, composition, lighting style.  \n- Typography: font family + texture/mood\n\n"
        },
